hackathon-eligibility:
WE'RE ONLY ACCEPTING BUILDERS.
Teams of 1-4 can apply to attend the event. All applicants within a team will be reviewed and vetted as developers or designers before they are able to attend the event.
Come with ideas not completed code. All projects must be built from scratch at the event.

hackathon-prizes.prize-content: We will be awarding slots in the LAUNCH Incubator for the top 4 LAUNCH Hackathon Projects. Admission into the incubator comes with an investment of $25,000 up entry and the option to another $225,000 upon completing the program***
A BB-8 and a drone for the top team chosen by Gigster
Nexus 6p 32GB device for every member of the winning team

Grand Prize: each winning team member will get a "Startup Starter Pack" which includes: Chrome Industries messenger bag ($160), iPad mini ($250), iPad mini keyboard case ($50), Apple gift card ($50), Amazon gift card ($150), One year free subscription to QuickBooks Online ($150)
For the companies who build the best projects incorporating the Expedia API
1st: Moto 360 Gen 2 for each member of the winning team + $1000 in Google Cloud Credit
1st Prize: DJI Phantom 3 Professional Quadcopter 4K UHD Video Camera Drone
Grand Prize: $5000—$2500 cash, plus $2500 valued ArcGIS Online subscription—for best use of Esri ArcGIS mapping technology
Grand Prize: $4,000 cash to the team which develops the most innovative and comprehensive use of the RingCentral API in their application
1st Prize: $6,000 cash for the best Hackathon project using a .CLUB name
Grand Prize:  Apple TVs (up to four) will be awarded to the team with the best Twitter integration, either leveraging the APIs or Fabric SDK.
Grand Prize: $2500 cash for best use of VoIP in an app
